# Guiding Principles

The Engineering Operating Model is:

* Product Agnostic
* Technology Agnostic
* AI Agnostic
* Specification Driven
* Domain Driven
* Test Driven
* Governance Driven
* Documentation First
* Continuously Evolvable

AI is an accelerator of engineering rather than the definition of engineering itself.

The framework should remain valuable regardless of the specific tools, programming languages, or AI technologies used to implement software.
